\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs24\sl360\slmult1 \sb60 \fi0 If a molecule for instance is excited to a singlet excited state {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ [{\i S}\\s\\do6({\fs20 1})]}}{\fldrslt }}
